  "identifier": "SB 0218",
  "title": "Bail, Bail Bonds - As enacted, establishes a presumption that a defendant should not be released on the defendant\u2019s personal recognizance if the defendant is charged with a felony offense that involved the use or display of a firearm or resulted in the serious bodily injury or death of the victim; requires a magistrate who determines that the presumption has been rebutted to include in the bail order written findings for each factor considered in making such a determination. - Amends TCA Title 40.",
